sql: SELECT id, SUM(black) AS sum_black, SUM(native_hawaiian_and_other_pacific_islander) AS sum_native_hawaiian_and_other_pacific_islander FROM demographics GROUP BY id HAVING SUM(black) < SUM(native_hawaiian_and_other_pacific_islander);

nl: Find years that appear at least 4 times in the data.
sql: SELECT year, COUNT(*) AS count_records FROM demographics GROUP BY year HAVING COUNT(*) >= 4;

nl: List ids where the minimum native hawaiian and other pacific islander is zero.
sql: SELECT id, MIN(native_hawaiian_and_other_pacific_islander) AS min_native_hawaiian_and_other_pacific_islander FROM demographics GROUP BY id HAVING MIN(native_hawaiian_and_other_pacific_islander) = 0;

nl: Determine ids where the average hispanic or latino total is between 50 and 150.
sql: SELECT id, AVG(hispanic_or_latino_total) AS avg_hispanic_or_latino_total FROM demographics GROUP BY id HAVING AVG(hispanic_or_latino_total) BETWEEN 50 AND 150;

nl: Identify ids where the total not hispanic or latino equals the total some other race.
sql: SELECT id, SUM(not_hispanic_or_latino) AS sum_not_hispanic_or_latino, SUM(some_other_race) AS sum_some_other_race FROM demographics GROUP BY id HAVING SUM(not_hispanic_or_latino) = SUM(some_other_race);
